## Emoji Vocabulary (Essentials)

| Emoji | Use Case | Format |
|-------|----------|--------|
| 🎯 | Objectives, goals, exercises | `## 🎯 Learning Objectives` |
| 📖 | Story/narrative sections | `## 📖 The Story` |
| ❌ | "Before" frustration states | `#### ❌ The "Before"` |
| ✨ | "After" improvement states | `#### ✨ The "After"` |
| 🚀 | Challenge extensions | `#### 🚀 Challenge Extension` |
| ✅ | Success criteria, checklists | `#### ✅ Success Criteria` |
| 💭 | Persona reactions/thoughts | `#### 💭 Sarah's Realization` |
| 📊 | Metrics tables | `## 📊 Success Metrics` |
| 🔨 | Exercises header | `## 🔨 Exercises` |
| 💡 | Pro tips, callouts | `💡 **Pro Tip**: ...` |
| ⏰ | Time markers | `## ⏰ 10:30 AM —` |
| 🤝 | Collaboration marker | `🤝 *Team collaboration*` |
| ⭐ | Exercise lead marker | `⭐ *You lead this one*` |
| 🧠 | Mindful/philosophical moments | `## 🧠 Mindful Moment:` |

*[See full file for complete list]*

