## Slide Generation — Critical Rules

### Separator Rule (CRITICAL)
- `---` MUST be on its own line, surrounded by newlines
- ✅ Correct: `</div>\n\n---\n\n<!-- SLIDE: Next -->`
- ❌ Wrong: `</div>---` or `---<!-- SLIDE -->`

### Slide Name Comments (REQUIRED)
Every content slide must start with: `<!-- SLIDE: Slide Name Here -->`
- Enables name-based lookup
- Nth `<!-- SLIDE: -->` comment = Slide N (1-indexed)

### Frontmatter Requirements

**All slides (Slidev):**
```yaml
status: active  # or archived
updated: YYYY-MM-DD
```

**Tech-talks & exec-talks READMEs:**
```yaml
status: active  # or archived
updated: YYYY-MM-DD
section: "Copilot Tools"  # Must match valid section (see below)
references:  # optional but recommended
  - url: https://docs.github.com/en/copilot/...
    label: "Description"
    verified: YYYY-MM-DD
```

### Valid Sections (from index-custom.html)
- `Copilot Tools` — Chat, CLI, Azure MCP, Code Review, Web, VS Code
- `Customization & Context` — Primitives, Hooks, Memory, SDK, MCP Apps
- `Agentic Engineering` — Agent Teams, ACP, Workflows, Journey, SDLC, Enterprise Patterns
- `Executive Talks` — Delivery, Economics, Labor
- `Workshop` — Modules 00–06

---

## Slide Design Constraints

- **Max under 25 slides** — Force focused, essential content
- **Layout:** NO per-slide frontmatter (`layout:`, `class:`, `transition:`)
  - Use CSS Grid/divs instead: `<div class="grid grid-cols-2">`
- **Visual style:** Dark cockpit with Tailwind CSS
- **HTML balance:** All `<div>` tags must close before `---` separator
- **Diagrams:** HTML only, no Mermaid
- **Ending:** Polish references slide + designed thank-you slide

---

## Archival Rules (LOCKED)

**Archived slides (`status: archived`):**
- ❌ NEVER modify, regenerate, or fix
- ❌ Agents must STOP if encountered and inform user
- ✅ Build scripts skip them; output remains deployed

**Archived talks:**
- Mark with `status: archived` in README frontmatter
- Content excluded from new work
- Archival rationale preserved in memory (events drawer)

---

## Slide Index Badge System

- **NEW badge:** Auto-applied to cards updated within 7 days
- **Data source:** `SLIDE_DATES` map in `slides/index-custom.html`
- **After any updates:** Run `node slides/scripts/sync-index-dates.mjs`
- **Check without modifying:** `node slides/scripts/sync-index-dates.mjs --check`

---

## Before-Submit Voice Checklist

- [ ] **Outcomes, not learning** — Shows what was built/validated
- [ ] **Metrics included** — 2-3 quantified improvements
- [ ] **Evidence-based** — Demonstrates through action
- [ ] **Persona-authentic** — Uses persona's unique lens
- [ ] **Professional tone** — Respects all as peers

---

## Agent Invocation (Keep Minimal)

When calling subagents:
- ✅ Trust agent config — they have copilot-instructions.md + their own docs
- ✅ Keep prompts concise: `"Generate slides for workshop/03-custom-prompts"`
- ❌ Don't repeat these guidelines
- ❌ Don't re-state voice rules

**Agents already know:**
- Repository structure
- Persona voices
- Slide constraints
- Frontmatter rules
- Section placement logic

