## Persona Quick Reference

See full file: `workshop/00-orientation/PERSONAS.md`

| Persona | Title | Exp | Quirk / Voice |
|---------|-------|-----|---------------|
| **Sarah** | The Skeptical Senior | 15y | "Drily skeptical" — won't acknowledge value without concrete ROI; her approval signals something genuinely works |
| **Marcus** | The DevOps Developer | 5y | "Chronically distracted" — half-present until tooling clicks, then snaps into focus; responds to workflow framing |
| **David** | The Seasoned Architect | 20y | "Pleasantly pedantic" — corrects framing before engaging; fears expertise becoming obsolete, not AI itself |
| **Elena** | The Quality Champion | 8y | "Professionally suspicious" — always asking about edge cases; QA engineer who needs AI to catch what she'd catch |
| **Rafael** | The Product Visionary | 10y | "Smoothly disengaged" — maps everything to OKRs, speaks in outcomes; ex-developer turned PM |
| **Jessica** | The Eager Junior | 1y | "Quietly terrified but quietly determined" — imposter syndrome, lights up when something clicks |

Full voice patterns and fears in PERSONAS.md.

