## Common Gotchas

1. **Slide separators:** Forget the newlines before/after `---` → parse errors
2. **Per-slide frontmatter:** Creates double separators → slide count breaks
3. **Two-cols layout:** Confines grid to col-left → looks narrow/wrong
4. **Archived talks:** Modify them anyway → breaks deployment
5. **Mermaid diagrams:** Use them anyway → visual inconsistency
6. **Section mismatch:** Use wrong section name → cards don't render
7. **Stale frontmatter:** Forget to update `updated:` date → badge system wrong
I
